data.description: This 4 bedroom, 4 bath home sits on just under an acre, with a privacy fence, 2 car garage, garden shed, 50amp RV hookup, solar, 2 HVAC units, and 2 decks. The main part of the house features a master bedroom and en-suite with jetted tub, multi-color led light with Bluetooth speaker and his/her sinks, walk-in closet, deck, a living room with built-in entertainment center, electric LED fireplace, a large, open room with bay window seating, coffee bar, a dining room that opens out to the deck,  laundry room with bi-fold doors and kitchen with pantry, lots of cabinet space, gas stove and built-in fridge. The 2nd part of the house offers the option for mother-in-law quarters, with a bedroom and full bath upstairs, 2 rooms below, a full bath and a private entry door to the backyard.
